'''Treta Zollarcos''' was a [[Professor/Legends|professor]] in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic's]] [[New Republic Astrogation Studies Center|Astrographic Studies Center]].

Following the [[Battle of Dathomir (Hunt for Zsinj)|Battle of Dathomir]], Professor Zollarcos compiled a report about the [[Planet/Legends|planets]] of the [[Hapes Cluster/Legends|Hapes Cluster]] as well as [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir's]] home system.

